contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|brak}} '''Brak''' may refer to: *[[Brak (African kings)]] (or Braque), former title of the kings in West Africa *[[Brak (character)]], a character on 1966 Hanna-Barbera cartoon ''Space Ghost'' **''[[The Brak Show]]'', a 2000 animated series *Brak, a barbarian character in a series of 1960s novels by [[John Jakes]] *Brak, a supporting character in the 1950s classic science fiction film, ''[[This Island Earth]]'' *[[Brak, Libya]], a city in Libya *[[Syd Brak]], South African illustrator {{disambig|surname}}
